<bridgehead class="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml:h3">ODS Weblog Automatic Hyperlinking</bridgehead>
<itemizedlist mark="bullet" spacing="compact"><listitem>If automatic hyperlinking is not desirable then whole post will not be annotated by putting only once &lt;no-auto-href /&gt; in the post body.
</listitem>
<listitem>The tag currently recognized by phrase-match api for no links is &lt;xmp&gt; and we need the phrase api to implement more tags as PRE &amp; CODE . </listitem>
<listitem>For multiple matches, only the first should be matched and turned to href link.</listitem>
</itemizedlist><para><ulink url="CategoryVirtuoso">CategoryVirtuoso</ulink> <ulink url="CategoryBlog">CategoryBlog</ulink> </para>
